<p><strong>SCP-CN-1554：</strong>无问前路，世间皆缄默<br />
<strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/scotoma" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3929032); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3929032&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609720564" alt="Scotoma" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3929032)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/scotoma" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3929032); return false;">Scotoma</a></span>，作者页在<strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scotoma">此</a></strong></p>
<div class="credit-back" style="text-align: center;">
<p><iframe src="https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--code/info%3Astyle/2" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="height:2em;width: 100%;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
